faq-one-content: The shipping fee depends on the delivery location and the weight of the item. We offer free shipping for purchases above a certain amount. Please check the shipping page for more information.
faq-two-content: Delivery time varies depending on your location. Generally, delivery will take between 1-7 business days after payment is confirmed.
faq-three-title: Can I return a purchased item?
faq-three-content: Yes, we have a return policy. You can return the item within 14 days of receipt if the item is in good condition and unused. Please visit the return policy page for more details.
faq-four-title: Do the products sold come with a warranty?
faq-four-content: Yes, all electronic products we sell come with an official manufacturer's warranty. The warranty duration varies depending on the product. Please check the product description for more information.
faq-five-title: Are there discounts for bulk purchases?
faq-five-content: We offer special discounts for bulk purchases. Please contact our customer service team for more information about offers and terms.
faq-six-title: How can I contact customer service?
faq-six-content: You can contact our customer service via email: support@tokoelektronik.com or phone: 0800-123-4567.
faq-eight-title: What should I do if I receive a defective product?
faq-nine-title: What should I do if the product I received does not match my order?
faq-nine-content: If you receive a product that does not match your order, please contact our customer service within 7 days of receiving the item. Include your order number and a description of the issue to facilitate the return or exchange process.
faq-ten-title: Do the electronic products sold include tax?
faq-ten-content: Yes, all prices listed on our website include tax. You do not need to worry about additional costs when making a purchase.
